      "rationale": "RHI comparisons at all five operating points yielded relative errors between 5% and 15%, within the pre-specified ±20% acceptance band. Pressure head errors were below 5%. Systematic conservative bias in RHI predictions noted and documented as acceptable for regulatory purposes."
